title: Ep. 71 " #PrisonBae " ft. @onmydink
description:
What if you got locked up at 17 years old and sentenced to a 20 year life sentence?! Had you even had a “real” sexual encounter? Is everyone getting gang raped in prison? How do you keep your head straight? Fast forward and now you’re out but when it comes to women your only sexual interactions have been a few nudes on a cell phone and
“hurry up before my mama comes home” sex. Our guest @onmydink has been through it first hand. He talks going to prison, what really happens inside, getting out early and finding love after lockup.
